OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCouncils opt for           
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'on-demand' buses in face  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fof cuts                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Councils are increasingly opting to    
OL,6, provide "on-demand" bus services to    
OL,7, plug some of the gaps left by cuts by  
OL,8, commercial operators.                  
OL,10,FThe County Councils Network, which     
OL,11,Frepresents rural councils in England,  
OL,12,Fsays three in four have rolled them    
OL,13,Fout.                                   
OL,15,FBut it warned that many services were  
OL,16,Fmaking a loss and extra funding was    
OL,17,Fneeded to keep them going in future.   
OL,19,FMore than half of journeys on public   
OL,20,Ftransport in Great Britain are by bus. 
